[section#sf.cmath.legendre
    [:en] Legendre polynomials
    [:zh_CN] 勒让德多项式
]

[%@library legendre]
[%@library legendref]
[%@library legendrel]
[:en]
[%Legendre polynomials[![$\mathsf{P}_\ell]]]
[%[$\mathsf{P}_\ell] (Legendre polynomials)[@P_l]]
[:zh_CN]
[%勒让德多项式[![$\mathsf{P}_\ell]]]
[%[$\mathsf{P}_\ell]（勒让德多项式）[@P_l]]
[codeblock:declaration]
double       legendre(unsigned l, double x);
float        legendref(unsigned l, float x);
long double  legendrel(unsigned l, long double x);
[codeblock:end]

[begin:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] These functions compute the Legendre polynomials of their respective
arguments [`l] and [`x].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数计算其相应实参 [`l] 和 [`x] 的勒让德多项式。

[para:returns]
[math]
[:en]
\mathsf{P}_\ell(x) =
  \frac{1}{2^\ell \, \ell!}
  \frac{\mathsf{d}^\ell}{\mathsf{d}x^\ell} \, (x^2 - 1) ^ \ell
  \text{ ,\quad for [$|x| \le 1],}
[:zh_CN]
\mathsf{P}_\ell(x) =
  \frac{1}{2^\ell \, \ell!}
  \frac{\mathsf{d}^\ell}{\mathsf{d}x^\ell} \, (x^2 - 1) ^ \ell
  \text{ ,\quad 对于 [$|x| \le 1],}
[math:end]

[:en@~] where [$l] is [`l] and [$x] is [`x].
[:zh_CN@~] 其中 [$l] 为 [`l] 而 [$x] 为 [`x]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] The effect of calling each of these functions is [?impldef effect of
calling Legendre polynomials with [`l >= 128]] if [`l >= 128].
[:zh_CN] 当 [`l >= 128] 时，调用每个这些函数的效果是[?impldef 以 [`l >= 128]
调用勒让德多项式的效果]。
[end:description]
